{"tid":424600,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曹星如21戰聲稱的王者對決 對手被爆是魚腩","createTime":"2017-10-05T01:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T04:40:00.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d96df07a4c072050f6c529f5de0a2d999fae98","tid":424600,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T01:28:33.000Z","msg":"向井寬史揚言第8回合KO曹星如<br />\n<br />\n31歲向井寬史來自日本大阪，20場賽中戰績13勝3和4負（3 K.O）。他於1月記招揚言會第8回合KO曹星如取勝，近日有在日本社交網站Ameba表示自信能於香港取得金腰帶，看來向井來勢洶洶、信心十足。不過，一眾網民記者會當日已極速向該日本拳手「起底」，發現他曾於2011年挑戰泰國的Pongsaklek Wonjongkam一戰中，甫開賽47秒就撞至頭部血流滿面，最終技術和局收場。其後先後對戰Srisaket Sor Rungvisai及同胞大森將平，向井更兩度需要拋毛巾投降，令網民不禁斥「魚腩拳手」。"},{"pid":"ed1d2758e3c7447a276946e50b4a2fe379751543","tid":424600,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T01:28:59.000Z","msg":"王者對決呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63eb1392b05759a1ef3ec78fac8acf618112cccb","tid":424600,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T01:56:27.000Z","msg":"河野成36歲，人地後生贏過世界冠軍，吹到對手係現任世界冠軍，唔goole都比你呃撚左。"},{"pid":"924a614247bebfc8b0183f438ca031d97f004780","tid":424600,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69386292dc397dc7df8a74c7b9012f0d3740b017","tid":424600,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"收手啦"},{"pid":"725566a55a642cbcec40db6c129557801a2e28ef","tid":424600,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a3ce0b3919e8b2dc099eb8ae1d84ffa26665abc","tid":424600,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim